{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-137-fibonacci-golden-nuggets","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-101-to-200","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 137: Zlatni delovi Fibonaccija","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Razmotrite beskonačnu seriju polinoma $A_{F}(x) = xF_1 + x^2F_2 + x^3F_3 + \\ldots$, gde je $F_k$ k-ti član u Fibonacijskoj sekvenci: $1, 1, 2, 3, 5, 8, \\ldots$; to jest, $F_k = F_{k − 1} + F_{k − 2}, F_1 = 1$ i $F_2 = 1$.</p>\n<p>Za ovaj zadatak, imamo ćemo vrednosti $x$ koje $A_{F}(x)$ je pozitivan ceo broj.</p>\n<p>Kao iznenađenje</p>\n<p>$$\\begin{align}\nA_F(\\frac{1}{2}) &#x26; = (\\frac{1}{2}) × 1 + {(\\frac{1}{2})}^2 × 1 + {(\\frac{1}{2})}^3 × 2 + {(\\frac{1}{2})}^4 × 3 + {(\\frac{1}{2})}^5 × 5 + \\cdots \\\\\n&#x26; = \\frac{1}{2} + \\frac{1}{4} + \\frac{2}{8} + \\frac{3}{16} + \\frac{5}{32} + \\cdots \\\\\n&#x26; = 2\n\\end{align}$$</p>\n<p>Odgovarajuće vrednosti za $x$ za prve pet prirodnih brojeva prikazane su ispod.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>$x$</th>\n<th>$A_F(x)$</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>$\\sqrt{2} − 1$</td>\n<td>$1$</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>$\\frac{1}{2}$</td>\n<td>$2$</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>$\\frac{\\sqrt{13} − 2}{3}$</td>\n<td>$3$</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>$\\frac{\\sqrt{89} − 5}{8}$</td>\n<td>$4$</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>$\\frac{\\sqrt{34} − 3}{5}$</td>\n<td>$5$</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>Naziva se $A_F(x)$ komad zlata ako je $x$ normalan bazni broj, jer postaju retki; na primer, komad zlata 10 je 74049690.</p>\n<p>Pronađi komad zlatnog narušavanja od 15.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f3f51000cf542c50ff08","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301765,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-137-fibonacci-golden-nuggets"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function goldenNugget() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\ngoldenNugget();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>goldenNugget()</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>1120149658760</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(goldenNugget(), 1120149658760);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-101-to-200","dashedName":"problem-137-fibonacci-golden-nuggets","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":true,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-101-to-200","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-138-special-isosceles-triangles","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-136-singleton-difference","id":"5900f3f51000cf542c50ff08","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"// solution required","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-137-fibonacci-golden-nuggets"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}